r, 95% of PwC=E2=80=99s U.S. workforce has spent over 360,000 hours on gene=
rative AI activities and learning, it said. =E2=80=9CThis is more of an ass=
istant that=E2=80=99s available to you than it is a search bar,=E2=80=9D At=
kinson said.=C2=A0PwC also developed a chatbot called ChatPwC, built on Ope=
nAI=E2=80=99s GPT-4 model, which more than 100,000 employees are using glob=
ally. Employees using tools like ChatPwC have reported a 20% to 40% increas=
