 Lightcap said OpenAI will likely work with other partners, but is currentl=
y focused on tapping PwC=E2=80=99s experience with enterprises and working =
with it to develop AI solutions for specific industries.I kid, I kid, they=
=E2=80=99re not literally rolling out a hallucination-prone chatbot to do t=
