eumann once ran to its creditors.Yardi, an engineer who immigrated from Ind=
ia in 1968, has quietly amassed a multibillion-dollar fortune over four dec=
ades selling property management software to commercial and residential lan=
dlords. Yardi Systems, the business he started with his wife Eileen, remain=
s family-owned even as its annual revenues approach $3bn. =E2=80=A6This is =
