n, but because you have some=C2=A0<em>duty=C2=A0</em>to somebody else not t=
o misuse their information. So if you work for a public company, you have a=
 duty to the shareholders not to trade on inside information before disclos=
ing it to them. Or if you are the <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbus=
iness.com/click/35548615.259324/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9=
