 would not require breach of an insider trading policy or employment agreem=
ent.=E2=80=9D But I suppose the company could *expressly waive* those princ=
iples, saying =E2=80=9Cwe=E2=80=99d love for you to trade competitors=E2=80=
=99 stocks, have fun.=E2=80=9D</p>
